cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with the task of matching spoken tags to visual instances, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes several models, which involves machine learning (ML) techniques, making cs.SD, cs.LG, and cs.AI likely sub-categories as well.
